" words to search" --> to make sure results only contains the exact word order

" words to search" -wordtoexclude filetype:pdf  	--> to make search results return pfd's only

site:wikipedia intitle:security  --> the results are only from wikipedia with title containing `security`

word | anotherword	--> using OR
(word | anotherword)	--> using OR and parenthesis
go to google.com/advanced_search	--> for advance options
